  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-01 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Higher model risk drives stricter credibility requirements; Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Full 13-factor assessment is included. This synthetic adversarial sample targets W-AR-01: one or more credibility factors declare a requiredLevel without a corresponding acceptanceCriteria field documenting the rationale for that level choice.",
